ultralife/types/VerificationLevel.title: VerificationLevel
ultralife/types/VerificationLevel.description:
Verification levels for pNFTs
 Each level unlocks more capabilities and carries more weight

anyOf.title: Basic
anyOf.description: Wallet signature only. Can create pNFT, view data. Cannot transact tokens.

anyOf.title: Ward
anyOf.description:
Ward pNFT - guardian-linked. For children, elderly, infirm, incapacitated.
 Transactions require guardian co-signature.

anyOf.title: Standard
anyOf.description: DNA verified. Can transact, claim grants, vote. Required for economy.

anyOf.title: Verified
anyOf.description: Standard + bioregion residency proof. Can propose, higher voting weight.

anyOf.title: Steward
anyOf.description: Verified + community endorsement. Can participate in multi-sig, emergency gov.
